      "text": "Key Design Principles:  🔒 Always-On (cloud enforcement, not home hardware)  |  🔍 Privacy-First (content IDs only, never message bodies)  |  👁️ Full Transparency (children know monitoring is active)\n📐 Age-Adaptive (3 profiles: 6-10 strict, 11-14 moderate, 15-17 guided)  |  ♾️ IaC-Driven (tofu apply rebuilds everything)  |  🧩 Modular (every component swappable)",
